snippet.title: Douglas Adams's Starship Titanic - Nightdive Studios
snippet.description:
Now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/467290/

From the creative mind of Douglas Adams. The Starship Titanic crashes into your house and takes off with you onboard. Inhabited by malfunctioning robots and a semi-deranged parrot, you must gain control of the ship and pilot it back to Earth.

Visit Night Dive Studios!
www.nightdivestudios.com
https://www.facebook.com/NightDiveStu...
@NightDiveStudio

Trailer:
http://www.lockevincent.com 
@lockevincent
